Naomi’s Champagne Garden

Dress Code

Glamorous • Green • Glowing — your outfit is your ticket to the garden.

The Vibe

  • Chic and feminine in shades of green — lime, pistachio, sage, olive, emerald.
  • Luxe textures: sequins, satin, silk, fringe, velvet.
  • Polished accessories in gold, champagne, or green.

Yes, Please

  • Mini or maxi dresses, halter or cowl neck, draped or fitted silhouettes.
  • Statement sparkle — sequined slips or beaded details.
  • Strappy heels or elegant sandals.
  • Gold jewelry, pearls, and chic shoulder bags.

Kindly Avoid

  • Casual denim, athleisure, flip flops.
  • Busy prints that compete with the green theme.
  • Overly casual tees/sweats.
Dressy glam is the goal — arrive glowing and camera‑ready ✨
